  "description": "<p>Manicurist (Full-Time) 美甲师（全职）</p><p>📍 Location: Westgate, Jurong East 地点：裕廊东 Westgate 商场</p><p>💰 Attractive Salary Package | 优渥薪资方案</p><p><br /></p><p>We are now looking for a passionate and experienced Manicurist to join our friendly team!</p><p>我们正在寻找一位热情又有经验的美甲师加入我们的温暖团队！</p><p><br /></p><p>What You’ll Do 你的工作内容</p><p>Provide professional manicure, pedicure, and nail art services</p><p>提供专业美甲、美足、彩绘等相关服务</p><p><br /></p><p>Ensure monthly individual sales/service targets are met</p><p>达成每月服务与销售目标</p><p><br /></p><p>Maintain excellent customer service and strong client relationships</p><p>维护客户关系，确保预约流程顺畅</p><p><br /></p><p>Recommend suitable nail care solutions or promotions</p><p>根据顾客需求推荐适合的护理服务或优惠</p><p><br /></p><p>Keep workstation clean and tools sanitized at all times</p><p>保持工作环境清洁，工具定期消毒</p><p><br /></p><p>Who We’re Looking For 我们希望你具备：</p><p>At least 2 years of experience as a manicurist or nail technician</p><p>至少2年美甲师经验</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Friendly, meticulous and customer-focused</p><p>个性亲切，注重细节，服务意识强</p><p><br /></p><p>Willing to work on weekends and public holidays</p><p>能接受周末与公共假期轮班</p><p><br /></p><p>Strong communication and time management skills</p><p>具良好沟通与时间安排能力</p><p><br /></p><p>Qualifications in Beauty, Hospitality, or Personal Services is a plus</p><p>拥有美容/服务类证书或文凭者优先考虑</p><p><br /></p><p>Bonus if you have 加分条件：</p><p>Previous salon management or team leadership experience</p><p>有美甲店管理或带领团队经验者更佳</p><p><br /></p><p>Able to upsell treatments or nail packages</p><p>能主动推荐美甲套餐或加购服务</p><p><br /></p><p>Why Join Us? 加入我们的理由</p><p>Friendly and supportive working environment</p><p>团队氛围温暖，互相支持</p><p><br /></p><p>Stable basic salary + commission and incentives</p><p>稳定底薪 + 业绩提成 + 表现奖励</p><p><br /></p><p>Career development and training opportunities</p><p>提供专业培训与发展机会</p><p><br /></p><p>Located next to Jurong East MRT (super convenient!)</p><p>地点超方便，紧邻裕廊东地铁站</p><p><br /></p><p>Apply Now 立即申请</p><p>📞 WhatsApp us at +65 9858 0286</p>",
